overview:
Corey is a aspiring IT Support professional with many skill sets, strong communications and over 10 years of experience working in business management.

He received his B.S. from University of Wisconsin Parkside, graduating Cum Laude in Management Information Systems and is a certified A+ technician. Prior to now, Corey received his Associates with Department Honors from Gateway Technical College in B2B Marketing Management.

Corey currently lives in Kenosha, WI. He is an amateur freelance designer, an avid fitness enthusiast and he enjoys going for long hikes with his girlfriend Maria and little dog Pinata.
